confidence: medium
comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-09T21:34:59.818Z",codex-importers,"2026-07-09 continuation: reusing this existing nonduplicate work item for dependency alignment, command-by-command production-like testing, agent-context UX evaluation, release/changelog verification, tracked/package/full-history privacy and secret audit, Greptile review, GitHub bot feedback, and green merge."
  "2026-07-09T21:46:38.151Z",codex-importers,"Preserved exact JSONL statuses, normalized kv values, made sync filtering symmetric/convergent, decoupled --status/--type from export filters, and clarified ordering/docs."
  "2026-07-10T18:58:32.762Z",context-specialist,"2026-07-10 context-specialist: Updated peerDep to >=2026.7.10. Untracked dist/ from git, standardized .gitignore (added .env.* and .agents/pm/extensions/). New untracked scripts/update-release-version.ts is a clean TypeScript refactor of inline node -e version-sync in release.yml. typecheck+build+test(117 pass)+pack(57.1KB)+changelog all green. npm@2026.7.10 published, CI+release green. No secrets in history."
notes[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-09T21:35:00.053Z",codex-importers,"Safety: preserve unrelated checkout changes; do not alter telemetry/observability; use read-only live APIs plus local mocks for Jira/Linear or any unsafe write paths; never log secret values."
  "2026-07-09T21:46:38.764Z",codex-importers,"Dependency baseline refreshed to @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.7.9, pm-changelog 2026.7.8, TypeScript 7.0.2, and Node types 26.1.1; npm install reported zero vulnerabilities."
  "2026-07-10T18:58:33.150Z",context-specialist,"Decision: Previous agent's work (jsonl kv normalization, lossless status preservation via resolveImportedTodoStatus, symmetric sync filtering, convergence-guaranteed empty-write, applyExportOrder copy fix) is production-ready. Extension version 2026.7.6 matches package.json."
  "2026-07-10T19:02:13.820Z",context-specialist,"CRITICAL RISK: scripts/update-release-version.ts is untracked in git, but .github/workflows/release.yml (also uncommitted) calls 'npm run release:update-version'. Both files MUST be committed together or the next CI release will fail with 'Cannot find module scripts/update-release-version.ts'. The last successful release (v2026.07.10) used the old inline node -e command."
files[9]{path,scope,note}:
  .github/workflows/ci.yml,project,audited free CI gate
